def sauvegarde(fichier):
    tmp = fichier
    App = xw.App(visible=False)
    book_open = App.books.open(fichier)
    book_open.save(tmp)
    book_open.close()
    App.quit()
    return tmp

def file_to_data_df(path):
    nom_colonne = ['Rang', 'Nation/Voile', 'Skipper/Voilier', 'Heure Fr', 'Lat', 'Long', 'Cap (30 min)', 'Vitesse (30min)', 'VMG (30min)', 'Distance (30min)', 'Cap (Last rank)', 'Vitesse (Last rank)', 'VMG (Last rank)', 'Distance (Last rank)', 'Cap (24h)', 'Vitesse (24h)', 'VMG (24h)', 'Distance (24h)', 'DTF','DTL']
    indice_colonne_dodge = [0,1,2,3] 
    indice_colonne_dodge_behind = 4
    data = pd.read_excel(sauvegarde(path),skiprows = indice_colonne_dodge, skipfooter = indice_colonne_dodge_behind, usecols = range(1,21),names = nom_colonne)
    data["Heure Fr"] = path[22:26] + '-' + path[26:28] + '/' + path[28:30] + "-" + data["Heure Fr"]
    data_df = pd.DataFrame(data)     
    return (data_df)

def nettoye_df(df):
    df.set_index(['Rang'], inplace=True)
    df['Heure Fr'] = df['Heure Fr'].str.replace("FR\n","")
    df['Nation/Voile'] = df['Nation/Voile'].str.replace("\n","")
    df[['Skipper','Voilier']] = df['Skipper/Voilier'].str.split("\n",expand=True)
    df = df.drop(columns=['Skipper/Voilier'], axis=1)
    return(df)
